Improved reporting when using --collect.

Now includes the docstrings for your test functions.

For example:

---

test_Dashboard.py:

TestCases:

test_logging_in_as_admin:

        This test will login as an admin account.
        

test__download_link:

        Tests the download link on Dashboard works, and then 
        checks that the actual download link on the firemeld page works.


---

Formats to HTML using pygments. To export, use (in terminal):

py.test --collect > file_name.html